Q. 3 tier architecture we used  in real time prod env for k8s micro-services deployment ?
--> yes, 3-tier architecture is absolutely used in real-time production environments, 
even for Kubernetes-based microservices deployments, though the implementation looks a bit different from traditional VMs.
